{% if isFramework("angular") %}

To create a custom cell editor, implement the `ICellEditorAngularComp` interface, which defines two mandatory methods:

- `agInit(params: ICellEditorParams)` - called when the editor is initialised
- `getValue()` - called by the grid to get the final value when editing is complete.

Full details of the `ICellEditorAngularComp` and `ICellEditorParams` interfaces are listed below under [API Reference](#api-reference).

{% /if %}
